      "text": "Last edit about 3 years ago by svayambhu108\n153\nNeeds Review\n153\nA-72 toward good acts + irrestably restrains him from evil, but for the person of Darkness the spirit of God does not compel toward the good + away from evil + so that person is lost! The Holy Spirit does not show him the way [of discernment, of discrimina Thus he is not of good from evil). This has to do with ontology: what saved. the person's nature is. The eschatological judge (is the one who] knows that nature, +, it would seem",
